      <p>Construction is cash-intensive. Fuel, wages, materials, rental. Every RM matters.</p>

      <p>RM34,000 down payment on excavator = 2 months fuel for fleet. Or 1 month wages. Or materials for small project.</p>

      <p>0% down keeps cash working. Not tied up in equipment deposit.</p>

