      <p>Construction deadlines wait for no one. Bank takes 3-4 weeks. Project awarded tomorrow needs equipment next week.</p>

      <p>We approve in 24-48 hours. Equipment on-site. Project starts on time.</p>

      <h2>2026 Machinery Budget Summary</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Plan equipment needs for the year</li>
        <li>Compare bank vs alternative financing</li>
        <li>Calculate total cost including down payment</li>
        <li>Consider used equipment savings</li>
        <li>Factor tax benefits into budget</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Smart machinery financing preserves cash flow. Gets equipment needed. Builds business value through ownership.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
